<h1>Review your action items and run the next retro</h1>

<p>
  Your retro <strong><%= @retro.name.presence || "Retro" %></strong> ended with
  <strong><%= pluralize(@action_count, "action item") %></strong>.
</p>

<p>
  Start the next retro to review those actions with your team and keep the follow-up loop going.
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Start the next retro", @new_retro_url %>
</p>

<p>
  Fast Retro will show previous action items when the next retro starts.
</p>
